Alastair Bishop from the Big Al Podcast joins The Clinch to debate Simon about the fights they both want to see happen most this year in the EFC (Extreme Fighting Championship). In the second of this two-part special, they go through Welterweight, Middleweight, Light Heavyweight and Heavyweight divisions and discuss their mutual desire to see the return of Mark Hulme and Garreth McLellan amongst many others. eNCA